<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1888" box="[2444,2592,2856,2890]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Mus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="253" pageNumber="858" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alticola">M. alticola</taxonomicName>
are uncertain, although it is probably most closely related to other endemic Bornean 
<taxonomicName box="[2061,2182,2978,3007]" class="Mammalia" family="Muridae" genus="Maxomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="253" pageNumber="858" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Maxomys</taxonomicName>
